data.description:
Gorgeous Home in Highly Sought After Lone Star Ranch Subdivision.  This Custom Built Home is One Of The Largest in this Subdivision Featuring Over 2700sq ft of Sprawling Open Concept Living Space!  NEW ROOF, Just A Short Walking Distance from the Community Pool! Courtyard Entrance, Entering Main Home is a Massive Foyer with 2 Huge Closets for Storage, Open Living Area with Vaulted Ceilings, Fireplace with Gas Starter Logs, Custom Kitchen with High End Cabinetry, Granite Countertops, Walk In Pantry, Stainless Appliances and Gas Stove.  3 Large Bedrooms, 2 Baths and An Extra Bonus Room That Can be Used as Extra Bedroom or Home Office. 
Primary Master Bath Features Walk In Jetted Tub, Separate Shower, 2 Large Walk In Closets, Split Double Vanities.  Extra Large Closets and Storage Throughout this Home!  Beautiful Landscaped Yard, Sprinkler System, Covered Back Patio, Side Entrance Double Garage.
